			<ul>
				<li>What is MDW?</li>
				<p>MDW is the site where people go to tell stories of their dysfunctional workplaces. If you've ever had a nightmare about work, only to wake up and realize it's reality, this site is for you.</p>
				<p>We promote the funniest stories and the ones that make you say "WTF?" If you hate your job, tell us a story why and maybe you and everyone else can get a laugh out of it.</p>
				<li>Who's behind MDW?</li>
				<p>MDW is created by a couple of guys who lost their souls to the corporate world. In an attempt to save their livers, they created a place to tell their ridiculous stories and commiserate with others.</p>
				<!-- Press releases here when they come -->
